PART: Habits
NAME: Habits
STATUS: draft

DATA: Habit List
MARKER: habit_list
INTENT: holds all habits and their state
TAGS: #date, #list
---
The app holds a list of habits. Each habit has a name, a completion status, and a creation date.

STRUCTURE: Habit Screen
MARKER: habit_screen
INTENT: the main screen showing all habits
TAGS: #list
---
The screen has a top bar with the app name, a scrollable list of habit cards, and a floating add button in the bottom right.

WHEN: Complete Habit
MARKER: complete_habit
INTENT: user marks a habit as done
TAGS: #card, #list, #user
---
When the user taps the checkbox on a habit card, the habit status changes to complete. The card moves to the bottom of the list with a strikethrough style.

ASSERT: Unique Habit Names
MARKER: unique_habit_names
INTENT: ensure each habit has a unique name
TAGS: #user
---
A habit name must be unique. A user cannot create two habits with the same name.

SURFACE: Habit Card
MARKER: habit_card
INTENT: labels and styles for habit cards
TAGS: #card, #date
---
The habit card displays the habit name, a checkbox for marking completion, and the creation date. The completed habits have a strikethrough style.